OL,3,CThousands of Next retailer workers win
OL,4,Clandmark equal pay claim
OL,6,FThousands of former and current Next
OL,7,Femployees have won a landmark equal
OL,8,Fpay claim against the high street
OL,9,Fretailer after a six-year legal battle.
OL,11,FAn employment tribunal has ruled that
OL,12,FNext failed to demonstrate that the
OL,13,Flower pay for sales consultants
OL,14,Fcompared to warehouse workers was not
OL,15,Fdue to sex discrimination, affecting
OL,16,F3,540 claimants.
