OL,3,CThousands of Next retailer workers win
OL,4,Clandmark equal pay claim
OL,6,FThe tribunal examined that between
OL,7,F2012 and 2023, 77.5% of retail
OL,8,Fconsultants at the retailer were
OL,9,Ffemale, and 52.75% of warehouse
OL,10,Foperators were male, according to the
OL,11,Fruling.
OL,13,FUnder equal pay law, employees doing
OL,14,Fwork of equal value at the same
OL,15,Fcompany must be paid the same unless
OL,16,Fthe employer can show that any wage
OL,17,Fdifference is due to a "material
OL,18,Ffactor" unrelated to sex
OL,19,Fdiscrimination.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
