OL,3,CThousands of Next retailer workers win
OL,4,Clandmark equal pay claim
OL,6,FIt ruled that the "business need was
OL,7,Fnot sufficiently great as to overcome
OL,8,Fthe discriminatory effect of lower
OL,9,Fbasic pay" and that "there must
OL,10,Fusually be a more compelling business
OL,11,Freason for such arrangements to be
OL,12,Fjustifiable".
OL,14,FThis is the first equal pay claim of
OL,15,Fits kind against a British retailer to
OL,16,Fsecure a win, stated Leigh Day, the
OL,17,Flaw firm representing thousands of
OL,18,Fclaimants.
