OL,3,CThousands of Next retailer workers win
OL,4,Clandmark equal pay claim
OL,6,FHelen Scarsbrook, 68, from Eastleigh
OL,7,Fnear Southampton, has worked for Next
OL,8,Ffor more than 20 years and was one of
OL,9,Fthree lead claimants representing all
OL,10,Fthe sales consultants in the claim.
OL,12,FShe said customer service was
OL,13,F"demanding" and often "undervalued".
OL,15,FIn a statement issued through Leigh
OL,16,FDay, she said: "It has been a long six
OL,17,Fyears battling for the equal pay we
OL,18,Fall felt we rightly deserved but today
OL,19,Fwe can say we won.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@KO]uD@WOUuD@cO]xD@POU
