OL,3,CThousands of Next retailer workers win
OL,4,Clandmark equal pay claim
OL,6,F"Anyone who works in retail knows that
OL,7,Fit is a physically and emotionally
OL,8,Ftough job.
OL,10,F"Customer service, in particular, is
OL,11,Fvery demanding and we do that in
OL,12,Faddition to lots of other essential
OL,13,Ftasks that go to make Next a
OL,14,Fsuccessful business.
OL,16,F"You become so used to having your
OL,17,Fwork undervalued that you can easily
OL,18,Fstart to doubt it yourself.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU
