OL,4,Clandmark equal pay claim
OL,6,F"I am so grateful to the judges for
OL,7,Fseeing our jobs for what they really
OL,8,Fare ` equal."
OL,10,FNext has said it intends to appeal
OL,11,Fagainst the ruling.
OL,13,FElizabeth George, Leigh Day's partner
OL,14,Fand barrister representing the
OL,15,Fsuccessful claimants, said the ruling
OL,16,Fwas "hugely significant" and the case
OL,17,Fwas "exactly the type of pay
OL,18,Fdiscrimination that equal pay
OL,19,Flegislation was intended to address".
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@MO]xD@EOUxD@XO]yD@EOU{D@dO]
