OL,3,CThousands of Next retailer workers win
OL,4,Clandmark equal pay claim
OL,6,FShe continued: "When you have female-
OL,7,Fdominated jobs being paid less than
OL,8,Fmale-dominated jobs and the work is
OL,9,Fequal, employers cannot pay women less
OL,10,Fsimply by pointing to the market and
OL,11,Fsaying it is the going rate for the
OL,12,Fjobs. We knew that already.
OL,14,F"The Employment Tribunal has confirmed
OL,15,Femployers must go further to justify
OL,16,Fpaying the different rates.
OL,18,F"They rightly found that Next could
OL,19,Fhave afforded to pay a higher rate but
OL,20,Fchose not to and that the reason for
OL,21,Fthat was purely financial.
OL,26,@nD@POUvD@AOUzD@AOU
