OL,6,F"It is worth reminding people that the
OL,7,Ffinancial compensation they will now
OL,8,Fbe entitled to is not a windfall.
OL,10,F"It is pay that they were always
OL,11,Fentitled to if Next had complied with
OL,12,Fits equal pay obligations."
