OL,6,FIn a statement, Next said: "The
OL,7,Ftribunal rejected the majority of the
OL,8,Fclaims made by the claimants, in
OL,9,Fparticular all claims of direct
OL,10,Fdiscrimination, and all aspects of the
OL,11,Fclaims made in respect of bonus pay.
OL,13,F"The tribunal expressed serious
OL,14,Fcriticisms of the claimants' expert
OL,15,Fevidence, and overwhelmingly accepted
OL,16,Fthe evidence of Next's expert and fact
OL,17,Fwitnesses.
OL,19,F"In respect of the specific terms in
OL,20,Fwhich the claim succeeded, it is our
OL,21,Fintention to appeal.
