OL,6,F"This is the first equal pay group
OL,7,Faction in the private sector to reach
OL,8,Fa decision at tribunal level and
OL,9,Fraises a number of important points of
OL,10,Flegal principle."
OL,12,FMore than 112,000 store staff across
OL,13,Fsupermarket chains Asda, Tesco,
OL,14,FSainsbury's, Morrisons and Co-op are
OL,15,Fbeing represented by Leigh Day
OL,16,Fbringing "similar equal pay claims,"
OL,17,Fthe law firm said.
OL,19,FNext operates 466 stores in the UK and
OL,20,Femploys 22,873 sales consultants.
